metadata.description: Beanbag Frens (BBF) is a community driven project containing Beanbag like characters, randomly generated as NFTs, on the Ethereum Blockchain. Our goal is to build the most heartwarming and welcoming community in the NFT space. Holding 1 Beanbag Fren NFT grants you more than a JPEG, frens will be able to be a part of an amazing community of 7777 other frens providing benefits and access to things such as IRL events, Metaverse expansions, breeding + tokenomics, physicals/merch, and more.
